Clone https://github.com/Royc4515/roy-carmelli-portfolio.git, then scaffold a Vite + React + TypeScript project inside it. Install tailwindcss with the @tailwindcss/vite plugin, react-router-dom, and framer-motion. Configure vite.config.ts to use the Tailwind Vite plugin. Replace src/index.css with just `@import "tailwindcss";`. Create this folder structure inside src: components/, pages/, sections/, hooks/, data/, types/. Create empty files: src/data/projects.ts, src/data/bio.ts, src/types/index.ts. Then run npm run dev and confirm it starts without errors.
